</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Meter / progress bar (<code>Shared/_Meter</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        One reusable bar primitive — <code>Shared/_Meter</code> partial — replaces three ad-hoc
        implementations (<code>.rev-progress</code>, <code>.fulf-meter</code>, <code>.rd-fulf-bar-*</code>).
        Width is always server-set via <code>style="width:N%"</code>; no client recompute.
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>Tones:</strong> <code>Hi</code> (green, ≥80%), <code>Mid</code> (amber, ≥50%),
        <code>Lo</code> (red, &lt;50%), <code>Accent</code> (theme accent), <code>Neutral</code>.
        <br>
        <strong>Layouts:</strong> <code>MetaLine</code> — bar + trailing inline text (intake review);
        <code>PctStack</code> — bar + right-column pct/sub (recipes grid);
        <code>BarOnly</code> — bar only, caller controls surrounding markup (recipe detail card).
    </p>

    <p><strong>MetaLine</strong> — intake review progress header (accent fill, surface card chrome):</p>
    <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4)">
        <div class="meter meter--meta-line meter--intake-progress">
            <div class="meter__track"><span class="meter__fill meter__fill--accent" style="width:77%"></span></div>
            <div class="meter__meta"><span><b>3</b> items need a quick look · <b>10</b> ready</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <div class="meter meter--meta-line meter--intake-progress">
            <div class="meter__track"><span class="meter__fill meter__fill--accent" style="width:100%"></span></div>
            <div class="meter__meta"><span><b>All set.</b> 13 items ready to add.</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:var(--space-4)"><strong>PctStack</strong> — recipes grid fulfillment meter:</p>
    <div style="max-width:200px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px">
        <div class="meter meter--pct-stack">
            <div class="meter__track"><span class="meter__fill fulf-hi-bg" style="width:90%"></span></div>
            <div class="meter__labels">
                <div class="meter__pct fulf-hi">90%</div>
                <div class="meter__sub">9/10 in stock</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="meter meter--pct-stack">
            <div class="meter__track"><span class="meter__fill fulf-mid-bg" style="width:60%"></span></div>
            <div class="meter__labels">
                <div class="meter__pct fulf-mid">60%</div>
                <div class="meter__sub">6/10 in stock</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="meter meter--pct-stack">
            <div class="meter__track"><span class="meter__fill fulf-lo-bg" style="width:20%"></span></div>
            <div class="meter__labels">
                <div class="meter__pct fulf-lo">20%</div>
                <div class="meter__sub">2/10 in stock</div>
            </div>
        </div>
